  <section class="lp-intro" aria-label="About ergoCentric">
    <div class="lp-intro__inner">
      <p class="lp-intro__eyebrow bbi-mono">About ergoCentric</p>
      <h2>Canadian ergonomic chairs for the full shift &mdash; not just the first two hours.</h2>
      <div class="lp-intro__body">
        <p>ergoCentric manufactures ergonomic seating in Concord, Ontario. Their chairs are specified by Ontario hospitals, contact centres, dispatch environments, schools, and offices where people sit for a full shift. The product range covers standard task chairs, 24/7 heavy-duty seating, big and tall options, and specialized clinical chairs.</p>
        <p>As an authorized ergoCentric dealer, Brant Business Interiors provides access to the full product line, trial chair programs, and volume pricing for large institutional orders. The 12-year mechanism warranty is the longest in the category &mdash; and we handle all warranty claims directly with the factory in Concord.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lp-diff" aria-label="Why ergoCentric">
    <div class="lp-diff__inner">
      <div class="lp-diff__head">
        <p class="lp-diff__eyebrow bbi-mono">Why ergoCentric</p>
        <h2>Four reasons institutions and dispatch environments specify ergoCentric.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-diff__grid">
        <article class="lp-diff-card">
          <span class="lp-diff-card__num">&#127809; Made in Canada</span>
          <h3 class="lp-diff-card__label">Concord, Ontario factory</h3>
          <p class="lp-diff-card__sentence">Every ergoCentric chair is made in Concord, ON. Canadian parts, Canadian service, and lead times that don&rsquo;t depend on overseas freight.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="lp-diff-card">
          <span class="lp-diff-card__num">12 yr</span>
          <h3 class="lp-diff-card__label">Mechanism warranty</h3>
          <p class="lp-diff-card__sentence">The longest warranty in the category. We file the claim and keep the chair in service &mdash; one call to us handles it from start to finish.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="lp-diff-card">
          <span class="lp-diff-card__num">24/7</span>
          <h3 class="lp-diff-card__label">Around-the-clock rated</h3>
          <p class="lp-diff-card__sentence">ergoCentric&rsquo;s 24/7 line is rated for continuous multi-shift use &mdash; specified by dispatch centres, hospitals, and security operations that run around the clock.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="lp-diff-card">
          <span class="lp-diff-card__num">OECM</span>
          <h3 class="lp-diff-card__label">Pre-qualified for Ontario</h3>
          <p class="lp-diff-card__sentence">Available under OECM Agreement 2025-470. Ontario institutions skip the tender process and purchase directly from Brant Business Interiors.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

