            <p>Yes &mdash; we can arrange trial chairs for institutional buyers evaluating ergoCentric for a large fit-out. Contact us with your order size and timeline. We&rsquo;ll coordinate a short-term trial and provide a quote that applies trial units against the full purchase if you proceed.</p>
